title: OTEP - The Ascension
description:
Otep (also spelled OTEP or OT3P) is an American nu metal band formed in 2000 in Los Angeles, California. The current lineup of the musical group consists of four members: vocalist Otep Shamaya, guitarist Aaron Nordstrom, drummer Brian Wolff, and bassist/background vocalist "Evil" J. McGuire.
